title: Jack Waltz, and You
content:

[[module css]]

}
.quote {
    background: #b8d4ff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    margin: 26px auto 0;
    max-width: 65%;
    min-height: 98px;
    padding: 24px;
    padding-top: 50px;

    width: 65%;
}
 
.quote:before,
.quote:after {
    content: "";
    height: 98%;
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
}
 
.quote:before {
    background: #b3cffa;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    left: -5px;
    top: 4px;
    transform: rotate(-2.5deg);
}
 
.quote:after {
    background: #afcbf6;
    box-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    right: -3px;
    top: 1px;
    transform: rotate(1.4deg);
}

[[>]]
[[module rate]]
[[/>]]

[[include component:image-block
| name=me.jpg
| caption=Most likely me, taken oh so long ago. I ache for those days again...
| width=200px
]]

Hi, I'm Jack. Jack Waltz.

Why am I here, you ask? Well, I'm not all too sure myself. I just feel like I exist in this world, of emptiness. I only feel nothing, the nothingness that exists around me. I know everything //is// there, and always will be, but... 

Does it all really exist?

Hm, where am I?

Why am I here?

I don't know myself, but, hm...

I wonder if I'll rot with time like the rest of them.

I guess I'm pretty ancient, something akin to a husk.

Sometimes, for the briefest of moments, I picture this //beautiful// sight...

A view of the infinite darkness...

A void, simply uncaring...

The luxury of being able to merely, not care no more...

And just sleep everything away, in an undisturbed slumber...

Truly a virtue, man shall never reach.

Speaking of which, was I ever a man?

Probably, though I don't quite remember...

Hm? Oh, sorry for going on like that, guess I forgot you were even here.

I'm fine myself. It's been a long day, I'm kinda tired. Though, how about you?

You'd like to know more about me?

Well...

I guess I've made lots here.

To me, it's like my own little smear in the grand scheme, no matter how insignificant.

I'm very proud of them all, very very much.

I think I should have a list here somewhere.

Ah!

There we go, just give me a second to put this all in order.

Here, just wipe off the dust.

And, that's it!

More is soon to come...

Or not...

...But I'll always remember my time here was a lot of fun!

Hm? Friends? Ah, I've got lots!

I'm sure I asked them to give me some quotes, now where might they be...

Oh, whoops.

That's a lot, let me pick those up...

All sorted. If I'm being brutally honest, I don't know half the people who wrote these!

@@ @@

[[/>]]
[[/div]]

[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Gonna use my quote to say how cool you are"//##

[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"I would kill Jack to gain his articles, but I just found out that he's been waltzing so hard he's immortal. Ah well, shucks to be Muffins, guess he didn't realise yet."//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user Machen2]]**, sharpening his Swiss Army knife.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Jack Waltz was hit by a drunk driver in 2002. What you see before you is a collection of works posted by unaffiliated artists, all conjoined under their similar pseudonym: that of the tragic victim of a motor vehicle accident. None of these artists have ever contacted one another. Please, respect the identity of what was once Jack Waltz."//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user rounderhouse]]**, lamenting my death.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"herggshsbdjwa!"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user TopDownUnder]]**, speaking the town of her people.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Stop it! Stop it with that whistling. Just let me out of here you sick fu--"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user AvocadoMilk]]**, in the dark room, resisting.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Listen, dammit! Jack is a fucking maniac, he’s got me locked in god knows where, along with Slurp, Hex, Top, even Afto... I-I think I’m the last one and I’m scared. My wife is Hannah Iverson, I have two beautiful daughters I want to see again, my home address is 2609 Charleston Road, Mountain View, CA 94043. Please! I’ll give you anything, god, just help me please! What's that noise? Someone's... Oh. Oh go--"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user MrIverson]]**, in the dark room, panicking.## [[span class="bblock"]]{{**this is a call for help i am stuck in the basment hes trapped me in here please come and help me please hes coming i hear the whistling please i dont want to**}}[[/span]]
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Heh, so in the end, I guess it's all of us who ended up in Jack's basement. Oh, that tune. Speak of the de--"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user Spherefinale]]**, in the dark room, attuning.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"{{Everything you hold dear, everyone you know and love, they are here. Come, they beg for you. Come to the basement. We are all waiting.}}"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user Jack Waltz]]**, {{whistling}}.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"I'm almost sure they can dance... almost."//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user Hexick]]**, tangoing instead of waltzing.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Cool author page, Jack."//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user T Rutherford]]**, breaching multiple 'Pataphysical layers through reality, just to add this quote.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"How do i add a quote?"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user slurppp]]**, googling witty quotes to use.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Weird things started happening when I didn't read his works. First, I dodged a flower pot falling towards me. Then, a massive spider crawled on my back and I swatted it off before it bit me. Then, I almost fell of a cliff! Please do what he says, as I'm afraid--"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user boxynton]]**, who is still very much alive, contrary to popular belief.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Have never seen him waltz."//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user OzzyLizard]]**, confused.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"He locked me in the basement with the rest of them. Everyone else, I'm with them. But they aren't moving. They're not even breathing. Why am I alive? Why'd he not get me? I'm hungry. But I'm not eating that black stuff on the walls, no, no. Something else. I want to eat something else. Oh. They've got to be edible, right?"//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user MrIverson]]**, in the dark room, spared.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="quote"]]
###000000|//"Basement? What basement? As far as I know, everyone's on vacation in Jamaica, Jack's treat. There's really nothing to worry about -- probably a very late April fools joke."//##
[[>]]
###000000|-- **[[*user BattleblockB0ss]]**, shuffling through a stack of $100 bills.##
[[/>]]
[[/div]]

@@ @@

That's all the ones I've got at the moment, but who knows, maybe I'll get a few more of them some time later.

Well, that was a nice talk. So--

Hm? If I... If I stop?

Well, I guess if I do go silent for a while...

...I'm more than happy to hand everything I've made to [[*user uncle nicolini]], [[*user machen2]], and [[*user moremuffins]], all great people I've met here, who'll be able to do whatever they'd like with my stuff! And everything I've co-authored will go to the respective co-authors, of course!

Well, I'm tired...

Mentioned I was tired earlier, didn't I?

Guess I might take a nap.

Well, see you later!

Let's see each other again, another time!
